address.streetAddress: Cleburne Plan, The Preserve at Singing Hills

location.fullValue: Cleburne Plan, The Preserve at Singing Hills

data.description: Welcome to your dream home!  A spectacular 4-bedroom, 3.5 bath extate that beautifully combines space, luxury, and natural charm.  In the convenient and friendly Preserve at Singing Hills, this home boasts awe-inspiring sunset views that promise to take your breath away.  Step inside to a warm and inviting foyer that leads to a grand living area, complete with a cozy fireplace for those relaxing evenings.  The living room seamlessy flows into a gourmet kitchen, a chef's dream equipped with stainless steel appliances, and an oversized granite island providing ample space for meal preparations, entertaining, or casual dining. Featuring four spacious bedrooms, each room offers a tranquil retreat. The main bedroom suite, an oasis of its own, has a lavish en-suite bathroom for ultimate relaxation. The remaining bedrooms are just as inviting and are perfect for family, guests, or home offices. The single-story home also offers a game room, ideal for hosting game nights or enjoying some downtime at home. The bonus room, flexible for your needs, can be the perfect spot for a home gym, office, or additional guest space. Step outside to your private paradise - a stunning outdoor area featuring a luxurious swimming pool. Picture yourself enjoying sunny afternoons poolside, hosting BBQs, or simply soaking in the picturesque sunset views from your backyard. With its spacious layout, luxurious features, and breathtaking views, this home goes beyond providing shelter and offers a lifestyle of comfort, relaxation, and entertainment. It's more than just a house; it's a place to create memories; it's your future home. Don't miss this opportunity - come and experience this marvel for yourself!
